graph LR
    CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator<br/>v1.15.0]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    CodeFlare -->|CRD dependency<br/>base Ray lifecycle| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.2.1<br/>REQUIRED]
    CodeFlare -->|certificate mgmt<br/>webhook TLS| CertController[cert-controller<br/>v0.12.0<br/>REQUIRED]
    CodeFlare -->|container platform| K8s[Kubernetes<br/>1.31+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    CodeFlare -.->|batch scheduling<br/>AppWrappers| Kueue[Kueue<br/>v0.10.1+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    CodeFlare -.->|OAuth proxy<br/>Routes| OpenShift[OpenShift<br/>4.11+<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|reads config<br/>DSCInitialization| ODHOperator[ODH Operator]
    ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|UI mgmt<br/>create RayCluster| CodeFlare

    %% Integration Points
    CodeFlare -->|API calls<br/>CRUD operations| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    K8sAPI -->|webhook invocation<br/>admission control| CodeFlare
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|metrics scraping<br/>8080/TCP HTTP| CodeFlare
    OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth] -.->|user auth<br/>Ray dashboard| CodeFlare

    %% Managed Resources
    CodeFlare -->|creates & manages| RayCluster[RayCluster Resources<br/>ray.io/v1]
    CodeFlare -->|creates & manages| AppWrapper[AppWrapper Resources<br/>workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta2]
    CodeFlare -->|creates| Routes[Routes/Ingress<br/>ray-dashboard-*<br/>ray-client-*]
    CodeFlare -->|creates| NetworkPolicies[NetworkPolicies<br/>Pod isolation]
    CodeFlare -->|creates| Secrets[Secrets<br/>CA certs, TLS certs]

